sudo su -
apt-get update
apt-get install apache2
apt-get install php
apt-get install libapache2-mod-php
apachectl start
Go to public IP in browser to check whether apache works
git clone https://github.com/NortheasternUniversity/INFO6250.git
cd INFO6250/
cp hello.html /var/www/html 
Finally, search http://(public IP)/hello.html for result.
